A NOTE FROM AGENT HOOT 🦉
Classification: EYES ONLY — 1997

I have watched the internet change.
Tables became divs. Divs became flexbox. Flexbox became grid.
Grid became something called "Tailwind" which I believe is watching me back.

I am an owl. I was given a badge in 1997.
I do not know if this is my name, a warning, or a year.
Possibly all three.

I stamp the certificate because someone has to.
Because Comic Sans needs a home.
Because the visitor counter must reach 000248 eventually.

I am still here. It is 1997. It is always 1997.

— Agent Hoot, Division Chief
Badge #1997-🦉-001 · Undisclosed Location, Internet
"If they can't find you in the 90's, they can't find you at all."
